[I] Efficient and performance-portable SIMD

[T] Highway is a C++ library for SIMD (Single Instruction, Multiple Data),
[T] i.e. applying the same operation to multiple 'lanes' using a single CPU
[T] instruction

[U] https://github.com/google/highway

[A] Google
